# SafeStep AI - Wearable Sensor Monitoring System

##  Overview
SafeStep AI is an AI-based wearable sensor system that predicts fall risk using motion data.

## Features
- Real-time sensor data simulation
- Machine Learning model (Random Forest)
- Fall risk prediction
- Interactive UI using Streamlit

##  Tech Stack
- Python
- Streamlit
- Scikit-learn
- NumPy & Pandas

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies:
   pip install -r requirements.txt
3. Run the app:
   streamlit run app.py

